Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.67,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限に生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:17.19,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限に生きられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.68,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て叶う
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:29.29,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもいろんなものがあたしを追い込んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:35.73,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きる残り時間　夢の座標　行方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:41.20,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部大事なものなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:47.56,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいさここらでちょっと甘いもの食べていこ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:56.56,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そういう思考停止ばかり得意になった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:16:02.37,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歩いてきた道振り返ると
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:08.26,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,イヤなことばっかりでもううんざりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:14.00,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触れるものを輝かしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:22.74,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな道を生きてきたかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:54.54,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常識ぶってる奴が笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:19:00.45,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次はどんな嘘を言う？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:05.64,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それで得られたもの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:12.00,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事に飾っておけるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:18.94,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも明日へと進まなきゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:26.32,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だからこう歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:38.61,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣いてる君こそ孤独な君こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:50.32,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正しいよ人間らしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:20:00.93,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落とした涙がこう言うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:25.68,日文插曲,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんなにも美しい嘘じゃない本当の僕らをありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------插曲结束-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么新曲是叙事曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合用于引诱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引诱是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前进行飓风行动时你没听见么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在学校里建了个摇滚乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在普通学生中非常走红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽然不会直接伤害他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有时也会利用一下他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而当他们妨碍作战时也必须立即肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们就在上述情况下进行引诱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这里的NPC还挺潮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也说明了她们的乐队具有这样的实力和魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 叙事曲可能有些不合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们都安静地听歌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不就不能大肆活动了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 那就弃用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么全体人员重新打起精神来开会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉上窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次侵入天使区域的复仇行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天后实施作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个作战么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是上一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次作战他也一起参与
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从椅子后面冒出来!？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是四眼田鸡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莉 你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东亚病夫怎么能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 不要以貌取人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么本大爷来试下你的能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你肯定没有朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 3.1415926
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,535897932384326433……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他就是传说中的圆周率帝!？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是四眼田鸡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人可是白痴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们的弱点都是一帮笨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做首领的别自灭威风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上次的入侵作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全暴露出了我们在头脑上的不足之处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次让前后三百年都无人超越的天才黑客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代号竹山的他加入作战部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对作战区域进行严密的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是真名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请称呼我为希伯来基督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧吧 这么酷的代号就这样被强奸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是优莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 天使区域是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是天使的住处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的住处?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底住在什么样的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那种地方会需要黑客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中枢可是电脑化控制的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 机械装置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里藏着通往神明的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是个不得了的作战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这个作战行动是第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使应该比上次更加有所警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GDM得要大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get Chance＆Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,angel beats！第三章\N My Song
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 状态不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像跟他们打成一片了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 但他们并不像第一印象那样坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是之前说的要大干一场的引诱行动么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 吓到你了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你认识我么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老是随身拿着把大斧头的前辈跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那家伙会招来不幸的 你可要当心他」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那混球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是占用体育馆没问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有问题的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前所未有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是不发通知的山寨演唱会 而是事先公布的演唱会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师们也不会放任不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会出现什么麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 听说这次作战必须要这样来聚集大批学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Girls Dead Monster啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你贵姓？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫优衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是个引诱部队里的小龙套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样我也知足了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是帮GDM的忙唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Girl Dead Monster很棒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简称GDM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清一色女生的乐队居然有那种演奏能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有作为主唱及吉他手的岩泽前辈的那种气场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她还自行作词作曲 我喜欢的歌是crow song
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌的桥段换调一气呵成 实在太赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且歌词也很赞 真不愧是岩泽前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最令人兴奋的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy　Alchemy呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没说完呢 Alchemy啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有时间跟我在这打酱油闲聊么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快为了你钟爱的GDM做苦力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说得对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我马上就修好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的热情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪能使那些学生们为歌疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不由得听入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你没有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的记忆也…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听了谁的记忆了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听了优莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的没有她的那么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么惨？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是唱不出自己喜欢的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲经常在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这片怒喝声中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲到角落缩成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堵住了耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在自己的空间里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上没有一片我的安息处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个时候 我看到了一个叫SAD MACHINE的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那个主唱也同我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在一个悲剧的家庭环境里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当感到痛苦的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用耳机堵住耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃进音乐的世界里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样试了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼似乎一下子烟消云散
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主唱在替我吼叫 替我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「强作正态的人才是错误的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「敢于哭泣的人才是正确的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「孤独的我们才活得像个人」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐喊 抨击 摧毁这个世界的荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的歌拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在一个下雨天的垃圾场捡到了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始了歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生原来还有歌 并非一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的成绩无论去哪间…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再依靠父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天天去打工攒钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一有机会就去唱片公司试唱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「毕业后我一定要离开那个家去东京」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「然后靠音乐生活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抱着那些想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可弹不了吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就别去街唱 休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我醒来后 我已经说不出话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头部挫伤 由脑梗塞引起的失语症
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是遭父母吵架的池鱼之殃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒命运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终逃不出去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一生就这样在此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 比沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等得＊花儿都快谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 那个是诅咒荒谬人生的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也经历了一场悲惨的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人害怕成为水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人们都在反抗神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不愿接受自己那么荒谬的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事就不要追究了吧 学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 GDM的演唱会是我们唯一的娱乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要剥夺我们的乐趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就像坏人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要以最精简编队进行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始时间为今天19:00
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是头等席哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 让我们大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 第一步室内侵入成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经进入天使区域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快把门关上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑就拜托竹山了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请称呼我为希伯来基督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个普通的女生房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做是犯罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子吃了三鹿发神经么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是女生宿舍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把灯关上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么电脑化控制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只有一台电脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一次没人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是展现我实力的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始解析
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 看来总算有点用处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这是侵犯隐私…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 安分点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢再来闹事 我就割破你的喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 亏我还对你们另眼相看 我真他妹的瞎了狗眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么少人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托再聚多些人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚开场就唱Alchemy？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我老老实实回到宿舍去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我一定要看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 倒是你们快滚回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学 让气氛来得再热烈些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 正是要靠我们的力量来造势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使已经出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在运行密码高速破解程序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 请称呼我为希伯来基督
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 竹山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复制所有资料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 请叫我希伯来基督…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把硬盘拆下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就暴露了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给我们看一下可疑的资料 竹山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希伯来基督
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生名单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们也混在里面么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是名单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有可疑的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果然只是犯罪行为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引诱部队被压制了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次作战也是毫无收获啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是为了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们的音乐是我们的精神支柱 求你们不要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直以来只不过是网开一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可别得寸进尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐器全部没收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是搞校庆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不会再给你们机会这样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个扔掉也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许碰它！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交给我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新曲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请称呼我为希伯来基督
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在意义就是这样不停歌唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我被那首歌拯救了那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我来这样继续拯救别人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩泽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总结一下得到的信息 优莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使原来是自我开发自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且跟我们生产武器的方法出奇地一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢断定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 太见外了 优莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说她必须采取跟我们一样的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个观点能推导出来的是最糟的设定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使为什么没有从神那里获得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么需要自己创造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩泽消失到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是让天使消除了么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是正在演唱中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是谁把岩泽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人那样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是她自己接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足消失的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来并不只是听从天使的要求进行规范的校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是能作为战斗力的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.32,0:24:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来比试吧 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop Dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是来代替岩泽的!？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组出个最强队伍来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.93,0:24:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到死为止都是谜团重重的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由衣喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在和谁战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的队伍没有报名参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.50,0:24:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比死还可怕的惩罚游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在发抖么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.84,0:24:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这球…真是爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.71,0:24:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四章 Day Game
